Package: GAMInflue
Type: Package
Title: Influence Analysis for Generalized Additive Models (GAMs)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alistair Dunn <Alistair.Dunn@OceanEvironmental.co.nz>
Maintainer: Alistair Dunn <Alistair.Dunn@OceanEvironmental.co.nz>
Description: Provides tools to perform influence analysis on GAM models fitted with the 'mgcv' package. Calculates standardized and unstandardized indices, performs stepwise term addition, assesses term influence, and generates diagnostic plots using 'ggplot2'.
License: GPL-3 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0), 
    mgcv,
    ggplot2
Imports: 
    stats,       
    tidyr,       
    patchwork,   
    RColorBrewer,
    utils        
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
